28	// Single case, ordain → summon → run → abjure, threaded through one body. The
29	// busybox vessel is consumerless — no nameplate holds its hallmark, so there
30	// is no committed regime file to carry the ephemeral hallmark across a
31	// case boundary. The hallmark therefore lives as a local across the steps,
32	// the same structural choice rbtdrc_hallmark_lifecycle makes for the same
33	// reason. This fixture IS hallmark_lifecycle with the registry-inventory
34	// middle (audit/rekon) swapped for summon + a bare container-runtime run.
